{
  "id": "adv_event_2410_01_04",
  "title": "星見市の\n人達へ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、麻奈がシーパラでライブをしたのは\nその一度きりになったが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ Mana performing a live at Sea Paradise\nonly happened that one time‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.85,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "同じ場所で琴乃達が里帰りライブをやることに\nなるなんて、運命を感じるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For Kotono and the others to do a homecoming live at the same place\nreally feels like fate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666666667,
      "endTime": 11.9596823375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……。私もお姉ちゃんに負けないくらい\nお客さんを楽しませられるように頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right… I also have to work hard so I can\nentertain the audience as much as my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1666666667,
      "endTime": 19.9769162814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "お話を聞かせてくれて、ありがとうございました\nおかげでライブに向けて一段と気合いが入りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for telling me that story.\nThanks to that‚ I'm even more motivated for the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1716781616,
      "endTime": 28.2816328047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それで……一つ思いついたことがあるんですが\nお願いしてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… there's something I thought of.\nMay I ask a favor?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.476394685,
      "endTime": 35.9966443379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだ。遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Don't hesitate to ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1914062182,
      "endTime": 39.0517916838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私達をずっと応援してくれた星見市のファンの皆さんに\n感謝の気持ちを表すような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To the fans in Hoshimi City who have always supported us\nI want to express our gratitude…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2580728848,
      "endTime": 45.9574139912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして成長した姿を見せられるような\n特別な曲を作りたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and show how we've grown as idols\nby creating a special song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.1521758715,
      "endTime": 52.1170284907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0784567833,
      "endTime": 54.0784567714,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1099.9974586000008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.0784567714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、シーパラだー！！\n今日は思いっきり遊んじゃうよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay~ it's Sea Paradise!!\nI'm going to play to my heart's content today~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9451209068,
      "endTime": 61.5784543991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.7784542401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "遊ぶのは構わないけど、はしゃぎ過ぎないでよ\n今日は曲作りの参考にするために来たんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Playing is fine‚ but don't get too carried away.\nWe came here today to gather references for songwriting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7784542401,
      "endTime": 69.66995070760001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 69.864712588
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.864712588,
      "endTime": 71.39387361210001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.5980459213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、急に琴乃ちゃんから\nシーパラに誘われた時は驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ I was surprised when Kotono-chan\nsuddenly invited us to Sea Paradise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5980459213,
      "endTime": 77.6966399192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 77.8980459213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "この間、お姉ちゃんの話を聞いて思ったの\n実際にその場で体験しないと気付けないこともあるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After hearing my sister's story the other day‚ I thought\nthere are things you can only realize by actually experiencing them in person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8980459213,
      "endTime": 86.42140216819999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがライブ直前にシーパラで遊んだのは\nきっとそれを感じるためだったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason my sister played at Sea Paradise right before her live\nwas probably to feel that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6161640484,
      "endTime": 92.2718554814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.4666173617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんはただ私達と\n遊びたかっただけな気もするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think Mana-chan just\nwanted to play with us though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4666173617,
      "endTime": 98.2051888148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.399950695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳だから、今日はみんなでシーパラを下見して\nここで歌うのにぴったりな新曲のヒントを掴むわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why today we'll all scout Sea Paradise together\nand get hints for a new song that's perfect to sing here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.399950695,
      "endTime": 105.7825584411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 105.9773203213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても、お仕事が忙しくて\n四人しか集まれなかったけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though with everyone's busy work schedules\nonly four of us could gather.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9773203213,
      "endTime": 111.7309936841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 111.943986988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだよね～。すずにゃんも「私抜きで\nシーパラなんてずるいですわ」って怒ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right~. Suzu-nyan also said \"It's unfair to go to\nSea Paradise without me\" and was angry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.943986988,
      "endTime": 120.75244531620001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.9439915656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんも「琴乃ちゃんと一緒にコツメカワウソと\n握手をしたかった」って落ち込んでたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan was also disappointed saying \"I wanted to\nshake hands with the small-clawed otters together with Kotono-chan.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9439915656,
      "endTime": 128.6043087958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.8106582323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "よーし！　来られなかったみんなの分まで\nシーパラを遊び尽くすよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! For everyone who couldn't come\nlet's play at Sea Paradise to our hearts' content~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8106582323,
      "endTime": 134.8296628633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 135.0439941088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "えいえいおー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hip hip hooray!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0439941088,
      "endTime": 137.13179461160001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 137.3106582323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……遊ぶのは構わないけど\nちゃんと新曲のことも考えてね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Playing is fine‚ but please\nthink about the new song properly too‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3106582323,
      "endTime": 143.1387329737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0668169975,
      "endTime": 145.1401513815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaisland-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 145.1401513815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2410_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、シーパラは楽しいね～\n行きたい場所が沢山あって、全然飽きないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh~‚ Sea Paradise is so fun~.\nThere are so many places I want to go‚ I never get bored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.0001564343,
      "endTime": 155.29702761960002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
